    According to NovaAI's internal roadmap (Q3 2024), NovaStream will include **Kafka Connect integration** to enable seamless ingestion and processing of real-time data from Kafka topics. This feature is designed to support low-latency streaming pipelines for use cases like event-driven architectures, live analytics, and IoT data processing.  
    
